; Tiny Walls fixture. Processing any Walls .srv in a run makes cavern's
; find_output_separator() mark '.' as a name character and ':' as a
; separator (commands.c update_separator_map_for_foreign_format), so every
; label in the emitted .3d — including the survex stations — uses ':'.
#UNITS D=Meters A=Degrees V=Degrees
#Fix WA 0 0 0
WA	WB	10.0	0	0
